Zambia’s Sata Orders Probe of FirstRand Purchase of Finance Bank

-- B y   A n t h o n y   M u k w i t a
-- 
2011-09-30T09:34:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-30/zambia-s-sata-orders-probe-of-firstrand-purchase-of-finance-bank.html
Zambian President Michael Sata
ordered a probe into the sale of Finance Bank Zambia to
Johannesburg-based  FirstRand Ltd. (FSR)   The government will also investigate  Libya ’s LAP Green
Networks’ acquisition of Zambia Telecommunications Corp., Sata
said in a speech today in Lusaka after swearing in Cabinet
ministers.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anthony Mukwita at 
